Paper Code: ETEC-452 L T/P C
Paper: Satellite and Antenna Lab 0 2 1


List of Experiments:


1. Setup an active and passive satellite link and demonstrate Link fails operation.

2. Study base-band Analogue signal parameters in Satellite link.

3. Measure S/N ratio, FM improvement and G/T.

4. Measure propagation delay of signal in a Satcom link.

5. Verify power distance relation.

6. Measure reflection coefficient/return loss of the given antenna.

7. Plot radiation pattern of the antenna.

8. Study Reciprocity Theorem.

9. Study current distribution along the element of an antenna.

10. Study polarization of an antenna.


NOTE:- At least 8 Experiments out of the list must be done in the semester.